summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing construction of Contract No. 5 of the Yesler and Atlantic Sewer Improvement Project to separate existing combined sewers in the area generally bounded by East Spruce Street on the north, 26th Avenue South on the west, South Judkins Street on the south and 30th Avenue South on the east and making an appropriation from the Sewer Improvement Fund therefor.
